{{Otheruses|other=一個已被[[棄用生物分類列表|棄用]]的[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]][[分類單元|分類單元]]|食蟲目}}

'''食蟲動物''' 是以[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]等小型[[無脊椎動物|無脊椎動物]]為主食的[[肉食性動物|肉食性動物]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://wordnetweb.princeton.edu/perl/webwn?s=insectivorous |title="WordNet - About Us." : entry on ''insectivorous''. |author=Miller, George A. |year=2009 |work= |publisher=Princeton University |accessdate=1 April 2010 |archive-date=2012-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120303174838/http://wordnetweb.princeton.edu/perl/webwn?s=insectivorous |dead-url=no }}</ref>。人類作為[[雜食性動物|雜食性動物]]，也有[[食用昆蟲|食用昆蟲]]的行為。

原本在[[哺乳綱|哺乳綱]]中一群以昆蟲為主食的動物被[[生物分類學|分類]]至[[食蟲目|食蟲目]]，後來的[[分子|分子]]分類學發現食蟲目是個[[多系群|多系群]]，其成員彼此之間並不親近，而是來自不同的[[演化支|演化支]]，現在該[[目_(生物)|目]]已被棄用。

雖然昆蟲體型微小，但卻擁有極多的種類（目前統計已超百萬種）<ref>Capinera, John L. (Editor). (2008). ''Encyclopedia of Entomology'', (2nd ed). Springer Reference. {{ISBN|1-4020-6242-7}}, {{ISBN|978-1-4020-6242-1}}. [https://books.google.com/books?id=i9ITMiiohVQC Ltd preview] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=i9ITMiiohVQC |date=20160624051424 }} in Google Books. Accessed on 1 Apr 2010.</ref>和數量，目前估計全球的昆蟲大約有 10<sup>18</sup> 個體，總質量可達 10<sup>12</sup> kg<ref>{{cite book |title=The biomechanics of insect flight: form, function, evolution |last=Dudley |first=Robert |year=2002 |publisher=[[Princeton_University_Press|Princeton University Press]] |chapter=Flight and the Pterygote Insecta |pages=3–35 |isbn=978-0-691-09491-5 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hTIMhD9BF1kC&pg=PA13 |access-date=2018-05-26 |archive-date=2020-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816084418/https://books.google.com/books?id=hTIMhD9BF1kC&pg=PA13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。某些不以昆蟲為主食的動物，也會在需要補充[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]的時期（如繁殖期）進食昆蟲<ref name="cascades">{{cite book |title=Field Guide to the Cascades & Olympics |year=2004 |publisher=The Mountaineers Books |isbn=978-0-89886-808-1 |pages=317 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5YQsJTwkD2AC |accessdate=2010-04-01 |author1=Whitney, Stephen R. |author2=Sandelin, R. |archive-date=2020-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816084423/https://books.google.com/books?id=5YQsJTwkD2AC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

食蟲動物廣泛分布於多個分類群中，包含[[鯉科|鯉科]]、[[青蛙|青蛙]]、[[蜥蜴|蜥蜴]]（如[[變色龍|變色龍]]和[[壁虎|壁虎]]）、[[夜鶯|夜鶯]]、[[燕科|燕子]]、[[針鼴|針鼴]]<ref name=echidnainfo>{{cite web |url=http://www.animalinfo.org/species/zaglbrui.htm |title="Long-beaked Echidna (Zaglossus bruijni)" (entry) |website=animalinfo.org |publisher=West of Scotland & Ayr Group |accessdate=1 April 2010 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422143139/http://www.animalinfo.org/species/zaglbrui.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[袋食蟻獸|袋食蟻獸]]、[[食蟻獸|食蟻獸]]、[[犰狳|犰狳]]、[[土豚|土豚]]、[[穿山甲|穿山甲]]、[[土狼|土狼]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hyaenidae.org/the-hyaenidae/aardwolf-proteles-cristatus.html |title=Aardwolf (''Proteles cristata'') |author=Holekamp, Kay E. |publisher=www.animalinfo.org |accessdate=1 April 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100417192844/http://www.hyaenidae.org/the-hyaenidae/aardwolf-proteles-cristatus.html |archivedate=17 April 2010 |df= }}</ref>、[[蝙蝠|蝙蝠]]、[[蜘蛛|蜘蛛]]等。部分大型哺乳動物也有食用昆蟲的行為，<ref name="cascades"/>其中[[懶熊|懶熊]]為最大型的食蟲動物。昆蟲本身也可為食蟲動物，例如[[蜻蜓|蜻蜓]]、[[胡蜂|胡蜂]]、[[瓢蟲|瓢蟲]]和[[螳螂|螳螂]]等。<ref>{{cite book |title=The economic importance of insects |year=1997 |publisher=Springer |page=198 |isbn=978-0-412-49800-8 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RKQIAqMyBJgC |accessdate=2010-04-01 |author=Hill, Dennis S. |archive-date=2020-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816084438/https://books.google.com/books?id=RKQIAqMyBJgC |dead-url=no }}</ref>許多[[靈長目|靈長目]]也為食蟲動物，包含[[狨屬|狨屬]]、[[檉柳猴屬|檉柳猴屬]]、[[眼鏡猴|眼鏡猴]]、[[嬰猴科|嬰猴科]]與[[指猴|指猴]]等。<ref name="JonesMartinPilbeam">{{cite book | title=The Primate Order | last=Stetoff | first=Rebecca | year=2006 | publisher=Marshall Cavendish | pages=92 | isbn=978-0-7614-1816-0 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=akbsqE8-ar4C | access-date=2018-05-26 | archive-date=2020-08-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816084444/https://books.google.com/books?id=akbsqE8-ar4C | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title= The Cambridge Encyclopedia of Human Evolution | editors=Jones, S., Martin, R., & Pilbeam, D. | year=1994 | publisher= Cambridge University Press  | location =Cambridge |isbn=0-521-32370-3}}</ref>因此靈長目可能源自[[夜行性|夜行性]]的樹棲食蟲動物。<ref name="Weiss&Mann">{{cite book |title= Human Biology and Behaviour: An Anthropological Perspective.| year=1985 | publisher=Little Brown & Co. | location = Boston |isbn=0-673-39013-6 | author= Weiss, M. L., & Mann, A. E.}}</ref>食蟲動物的食物還可包括[[蜘蛛|蜘蛛]]、[[蜈蚣|蜈蚣]]、[[蚯蚓|蚯蚓]]等在分類學上不屬於昆蟲的動物。
